            <title><![CDATA[Popular Steam Game Lowers DLC Price Due To Everything Else Getting More Expensive]]></title>
            <link>https://kotaku.com/everspace-2-wrath-of-the-ancients-expansion-price-lower-1851776712</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/popular-steam-game-lowers-dlc-price-due-to-everything-else-getting-more-expensive.1167780/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://kotaku.com/everspace-2-wrath-of-the-ancients-expansion-price-lower-1851776712<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p><em>Everspace 2'</em>s upcoming paid expansion is set to launch in May. But it will cost a bit less than originally announced, and the devs cite the <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/switch-2-price-trump-tariffs-vietnam-china-trade-war-1851774438&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/switch-2-price-trump-tariffs-vietnam-china-trade-war-1851774438">ongoing economic crisis in the world</a></span> as the reason for the discount. </p><div><h4>Suggested Reading</h4></div><div data-video-id="196013" data-monetizable="true" data-position="sidebar" data-video-title="The Top 10 Most-Played Games On Steam Deck: October 2023 Edition" data-video-blog-id="9" data-video-network="kotaku" data-video-duration="316" data-playlist="196013,196358,196663" data-current="196013"><div><p>The Top 10 Most-Played Games On Steam Deck: October 2023 Edition</p></div><video disablepictureinpicture="" muted="" playsinline="" width="100%" height="100%" crossorigin="anonymous" preload="none"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/196013/196013_240p.mp4" label="240p" type="video/mp4"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/196013/196013_480p.mp4" label="480p" type="video/mp4"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/196013/196013_720p.mp4" label="720p" type="video/mp4"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/196013/196013_1080p.mp4" label="1080p" type="video/mp4"><track kind="captions" label="English" src="https://kinja.com/api/videoupload/caption/21533.vtt" srclang="en"></video><div><ul><li data-label="">Off</li><li data-label="English">English</li></ul></div></div><div><h4>Suggested Reading</h4></div><p>2023's <em>Everspace 2 </em>is a popular and fun spaceship-based looter shooter that has received big and small updates over the last two years. But its next big update, <em>Wrath of the Ancients</em>, is the game’s largest expansion. It is set to add new quests, places to explore, ships, items, and more to the game. <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1128920/view/524213474678538448&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1128920/view/524213474678538448" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Originally, as announced earlier this month</a></span>, the plan was to sell this expansion for $30. However, due to so many things “getting more expensive” these days, the developers have decided to knock $5 off the price. </p><p>“With events happening in the world, it seems like everything is getting more expensive and there’s a lot of uncertainty in general,” <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1128920/view/524214742651240614&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1128920/view/524214742651240614" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">said <em>Everspace 2</em> developer Rockfish Games in a Steam post on April 16</a></span>. “You feel it, we feel it, and all those marketing emails we’ve all been hammered with talking about prices going up certainly don’t help. Let’s change that!”</p><p>Rockfish explained that after getting together to chat and “reassess” things, the team has decided to lower the price of <em>Wrath of the Ancients</em> from $30 to $25. In the Steam post announcing this price change, the devs made it clear that nothing is being cut from the DLC. </p><p>It was also announced that a previously released DLC, <em>Titans</em>, was getting a price drop, too. <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://store.steampowered.com/app/2873460/EVERSPACE_2__Titans/&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2873460/EVERSPACE_2__Titans/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><em>Titans </em>launched at $15 but now costs $12</a></span>. The team says it will have a new artbook and soundtrack available for players who had already set aside the $30 and now might have an extra $5 to spare. However, the team knows that for many people, that money is likely going to be spent elsewhere. </p><p>“If that fiver means more ramen in your pantry, we get and respect that,” said the studio. “Do your part by spreading the word about <em>Everspace 2: Wrath of the Ancients</em> and give us a positive review if you like what you’ve played. It helps!”</p><p>Just this week we saw <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/sony-price-increase-ps-plus-canada-mexico-ps5-tariffs-1851776655&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/sony-price-increase-ps-plus-canada-mexico-ps5-tariffs-1851776655">Sony raise the price of PS Plus</a></span> and <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/ps5-digital-edition-price-increase-uk-europe-tariffs-1851776054?rev=1744645898815&amp;_gl=1*9iem4g*_ga*NzE0NzM5NTc5LjE3Mjk4Njg5MzU.*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTc0NDkxMzQ4Mi4zMDkuMS4xNzQ0OTE0NzA5LjMwLjAuMA..&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/ps5-digital-edition-price-increase-uk-europe-tariffs-1851776054?rev=1744645898815&amp;_gl=1*9iem4g*_ga*NzE0NzM5NTc5LjE3Mjk4Njg5MzU.*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTc0NDkxMzQ4Mi4zMDkuMS4xNzQ0OTE0NzA5LjMwLjAuMA..">PS5 consoles in multiple countries</a></span>. <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/mario-kart-world-switch-2-price-80-nintendo-direct-1851774262&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/mario-kart-world-switch-2-price-80-nintendo-direct-1851774262">Nintendo is charging $80 for a single video game</a></span>. <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.cbsnews.com/news/grocery-prices-inflation-metro-areas-cities-smartasset/&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.cbsnews.com/news/grocery-prices-inflation-metro-areas-cities-smartasset/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">And grocery prices in many cities are going up and up</a></span> as Trump’s tariffs continue to cause chaos across the global market. </p><p><em>Everspace 2: Wrath of the Ancients</em> launches on consoles and PC on May 12.  </p><p> .<br></p></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
